{"tid":465983,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Face ID 有漏洞？唔係 Twins 都可以解鎖！","createTime":"2017-11-12T06:32:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T09:11:15.000Z","uid":72186,"like":8,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"b50f711332a98a99335f6c92e5b239128494eee0","tid":465983,"uid":72186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T06:32:11.000Z","msg":"Man Unlocks The IPhone X Of His Brother By Face ID. Spoiler Alert: They Are Not Twins!<br />\n<a href=\"https://amp.i4u.com/2017/11/125450/man-unlocks-iphone-x-his-brother-face-id-spoiler-alert-they-are-not-twins\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Famp.i4u.com%2F2017%2F11%2F125450%2Fman-unlocks-iphone-x-his-brother-face-id-spoiler-alert-they-are-not-twins&d=m0e3U0I%2B%2Bcs63X%2BT%2FLg42p4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=e1f56672\" target=\"_blank\">https://amp.i4u.com/2017/11/125450/man-unlocks-iphone-x-his-brother-face-id-spoiler-alert-they-are-not-twins</a><br />\n<br />\n片段在 Reddit 討論區上載引起了不少網民關注，兩名兄弟年齡相差 5 歲，首先大哥成功利用 Face ID 解鎖，之後他將 iPhone X 交予弟弟，起初弟弟沒有戴眼鏡，iPhone X 並不接受，但當他戴上眼鏡後，iPhone X 則順利解鎖。有網民認為 Face ID 和是否佩戴眼鏡無關，估計是系統有漏洞所致。<br />\n<br />\n拍攝者後來留言，表示重設 Face ID 後再次嘗試，發現漏洞仍然有 50% 機會出現。大哥首先設定 Face ID，然後以面容解鎖。弟弟接著將手機對著自己並以密碼解鎖，再將 iPhone X 上鎖。接下來將 iPhone X 舉起，Face ID 成功解鎖，之後每次他舉起 iPhone X 都能夠以面容解鎖。不過他表示反覆試驗後，發現類似情況並非每次都出現，漏洞出現的比例約一半一半。<br />\n<br />\n中文報導:ePrice<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cRzUaeCLJi8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcRzUaeCLJi8&d=m0e3U0I%2B%2Bcs63X%2BT%2FLg42p4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=9631c640\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cRzUaeCLJi8</a>"},{"pid":"fd439f96b5bd76a26a07e45b0a3ddd07a80fca4f","tid":465983,"uid":48577,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T06:33:58.000Z","msg":"以為有黑飽睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75577c257aefc3802e227a4779b70f9c4ddad10a","tid":465983,"uid":72186,"li